title: 195 - From the Heart of Italy, It’s Fazoleenies
description: Today’s episode of The POD kicks off with a full hause of characters discussing the greatest fast food money can buy. With the rather candid start the boys then jump into the POD Fod, which is a folder compiled of all things around the internet. Today’s FOD includes some “Boobs for Boosters”, expert ham sniffers, an absolutely YOKED Jeff Bezos and much much more. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you Wednesday, Cheers.
